<subSubSection box="[199,1186,655,680]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="36.[151,1436,151,751]" box="[199,1186,655,680]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,656,680]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" reason="1">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is descriptive for the distinctive medial process on the aedeagus.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="discussion">
