</taxonomicName>
<emphasis box="[1114,1121,692,715]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">,</emphasis>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1130,1222,692,716]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1130,1222,692,716]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
and can be distinguished by the prominent, laminate process on the aedeagus.
</paragraph>
